values:
We also made a special trip down through the kitchens for non-perishables late last night, boys and girls, and stocked up on quite a horde -- not even getting into all we got in Hogsmeade the day before.  It'll be a splendid party for all!  Our gift to our dear youngest brother: half the stock of Honeydukes' wares, delivered straight from the source!  And a few right surprises we made up all on our own...

--Gred & Forge
